rea Scouts]]\n|[[Brooklyn, New York]]\n|Classic\n|1963\n|\n|-\n|[[Bethesda Emerald Knights]]\n|[[Saratoga Springs, New York]]\n|Modern\n|1974\n|\n|-\n|[[Beverly Cardinals]]\n|[[Beverly, Massachusetts]]\n|Classic/Modern\n|1968&ndash;1974\n|{{Official website | http://www.cardinaldrumandbuglecorps.com/index.html}}\n|-\n|[[Beverly Crusaders]]\n|[[Beverly, Massachusetts]]\n|Classic\n|1954&ndash;1957\n|{{Official website | http://www.cardinaldrumandbuglecorps.com/index.html}}\n|-\n|[[Big Sky Reveliers]]\n|[[Billings, Montana]]\n|Classic/Modern\n|1969&ndash;1972\n|\n|-\n|[[Big Tree Emeralds]]\n|[[Blasdell, New York]]\n|Classic\n|1954\n|\n|-\n|[[Bishop's Rock (Drum Corps)|Bishop's Rock]]\n|[[Hopatcong, New Jersey]]\n|Modern\n|1999\n|\n|-\n|[[Black Barons (drum corps)|Black Barons]]\n|[[Malden, Massachusetts]]\n|\n|?\n|\n|-\n|[[Black Diamond Regiment]]\n|[[Schuylkill Haven, Pennsylvania]]\n|Modern\n|1977&ndash;1979\n|\n|-\n|[[Black Diamonds (Drum Corps)|Black Diamonds]]\n|[[Pensacola, Florida]]\n|Classic/Modern\n|1969&ndash;1978\n|\n|-\n|[[Black Gold (Drum Corps)|Black Gold]]\n|[[Tulsa, Oklahoma]]\n|Modern\n|1985&ndash;1993\n|\n|-\n|[[Black Hawks (NJ)]]\n|[[East Brunswick, New Jersey]]\n|\n|?\n|\n|-\n|[[Black Hawks (WI)]]\n|[[LaCrosse, Wisconsin|La Crosse, Wisconsin]]\n|\n|?\n|\n|-\n|[[Belleville Black Knights (IL)]]\n|[[Belleville, Illinois]]\n|Classic/Modern\n|1953&ndash;1989\n|{{Official website | https://web.archive.org/web/20080912013203/http://www.geocities.com/semccarty/BellevilleBlackKnights.html}}\n|-\n|[[Black Knights (NY)]]\n|[[Oswego, New York]]\n|Modern\n|1975\n|\n|-\n|[[Black Ravens]]\n|[[Brooklyn, New York]]\n|\n|?\n|\n|-\n|[[Black Shields Of Sparta]]\n|[[Mount Carmel, Ohio]]\n|Classic\n|1968\n|\n|-\n|[[Black Watch (WA)]]\n|[[Auburn, Washington]]\n|Classic/Modern\n|1971&ndash;1982\n|\n|-\n|[[Black Watch (NJ)]]\n|[[Willingboro, New Jersey]]\n|Classic/Modern\n|1966&ndash;1983\n|\n|-\n|[[Blackhawk Voyageurs]]\n|[[Beloit/Janesville, Wisconsin]]\n|Modern\n|1973&nd