-Bons)]]\n|[[Audubon, New Jersey]]\n|Classic/Modern\n|1938&ndash;1978\n|{{Official website | http://members.aol.com/_ht_a/chickie0464/index.html}}\n|-\n|[[Aurora Express]]\n|[[East Aurora (Buffalo), New York]]\n|Modern\n|1984-1992\n|\n|-\n|[[Austin Grenadiers]]\n|[[Chicago, Illinois]]\n|\n|?\n|\n|-\n|[[Austin (Spamtown) Lancers]]\n|[[Austin, Minnesota]]\n|Classic\n|1957&ndash;1963\n|\n|-\n|[[Avant Garde (Drum Corps)|Avant Garde]]\n|[[Saratoga Springs, New York]]\n|Modern\n|1975&ndash;1985\n|{{Official website | http://avantgardealumni.org}}\n|-\n|[[Baladins]]\n|[[Saint-Jean-sur-Richelieu, Quebec|St. Jean, Quebec]]\n|\n|?\n|\n|-\n|[[Ballantine (Drum Corps)|Ballantine]]\n|[[Newark, New Jersey]]\n|\n|?\n|\n|-\n|[[Baltimore Police Post Sons Of Veterans VFW]]\n|[[Baltimore, Maryland]]\n|Classic\n|?\n|\n|-\n|[[Bandettes]]\n|[[Sault Ste. Marie, Ontario]]\n|Classic/Modern\n|1963&ndash;2004\n|\n|-\n|[[Bangor Falcons]]\n|[[Bangor, Wisconsin]]\n|\n|?\n|\n|-\n|[[Barons (Drum Corps)|Barons]]\n|[[Chicopee, Massachusetts]]\n|\n|?\n|\n|-\n|[[Barons of Steuben]]\n|[[Corning (city), New York|Corning, New York]]\n|Classic/Modern\n|1966&ndash;1982\n|\n|-\n|[[Barringer-Walker Cadets]]\n|[[Newark, New Jersey]]\n|\n|?\n|\n|-\n|[[Bath Cadets]]\n|[[Bath, Maine]]\n|\n|?\n|\n|-\n|[[Bayonne Bridgeman]]\n|[[Bayonne, New Jersey]]\n|\n|?\n|<ref>https://www.nj.com/bayonne/2012/06/bayonnes_bridgemen_org_will_be.html</ref><ref>http://bridgemenpa.org/History.html</ref><ref>https://www.tapinto.net/towns/bayonne/sections/arts-and-entertainment/articles/bridgemen-complete-bayonne-run-with-rousing-final</ref>\n|-\n|[[BC Ambassadors]]\n|[[Richmond, British Columbia]]\n|\n|?\n|\n|-\n|[[Bedford Militiamen]]\n|[[Bedford, Massachusetts]]\n|\n|?\n|\n|-\n|[[Bellaires]]\n|[[Bellmawr, New Jersey]]\n|\n|?\n|\n|-\n|[[Belles of St. John]]\n|[[Brantford, Ontario]]\n|Modern\n|1974&ndash;1976\n|\n|-\n|[[Belles of St. Mary's (WI)]]\n|[[Rhinelander, Wisconsin]]\n|Classic/Modern\n|1967&ndash;1976\n|\n|-\n|[[Belles of St. 