ates]]\n|[[Bluffton, Indiana]]\n|\n|?\n|\n|-\n|[[Bonnies]]\n|[[New Britain, Connecticut]]\n|\n|?\n|\n|-\n|[[Bordentown Little Devils]]\n|[[Bordentown, New Jersey]]\n|Classic\n|1959&ndash;1968\n|\n|-\n|[[Boston Crusaders Drum and Bugle Corps|Boston Crusaders]]<ref group=\"notes\">Formerly known as Most Precious Blood Crusaders; Hyde Park Crusaders; Boston</ref>\n|[[Boston, Massachusetts]]\n|Classic/Modern\n|1940&ndash;present\n|{{Official website | http://www.crusaders.com}}\n|-\n|[[Boy Scout Troup No. 63]]\n|[[Michigan]]\n|\n|?\n|\n|-\n|[[Boys Club Gents]]\n|\n|\n|?\n|\n|-\n|[[Boys of Syracuse Post 41]]\n|[[Syracuse, New York]]\n|\n|?\n|\n|-\n|[[Bracken Cavaliers]]\n|[[Bristol, Pennsylvania]]\n|Classic/Modern\n|1922&ndash;1999\n|\n|-\n|[[Braintree Braves]]\n|[[Braintree, Massachusetts]]\n|Classic/Modern\n|1943&ndash;1997\n|\n|-\n|[[Braintree Warriors]]\n|[[Braintree, Massachusetts]]\n|Classic\n|1943&ndash;1972\n|\n|-\n|[[Brampton Senators]]\n|[[Brampton]], [[Ontario]]\n|\n|?\n|\n|-\n|[[Brantford Girls Drum and Bugle Corp]]\n|[[Brantford, Ontario]]\n|Classic\n|1981&ndash;1985\n|{{Official website | http://stjohnsdrumcorpsalumni.com/history.html}}\n|-\n|[[Brass Majesticks]]\n|[[New Jersey]]\n|\n|?\n|\n|-\n|[[Brass Regiment]]\n|[[Park Falls, Wisconsin]]\n|Classic\n|1971\n|\n|-\n|[[Brassmen]]\n|[[Bellingham, Washington]]\n|Modern\n|1984\n|\n|-\n|[[Bridgemen]]\n|[[Bayonne, New Jersey]]\n|Classic/Modern\n|1964&ndash;1988\n|{{Official website | http://www.bridgemen.com}}\n|-\n|[[Bridgeport PAL (Police Athletic League) Cadets]]\n|[[Bridgeport, Connecticut]]\n|Classic\n|1951&ndash;1967\n|{{Official website | http://www.palcadets.org}}\n|-\n|[[Brigade (Drum Corps)|Brigade]]\n|[[Highland Park, Illinois]]\n|Classic\n|1964\n|\n|-\n|[[Brigadiers]]\n|[[Blackwood, New Jersey]]\n|\n|?\n|\n|-\n|[[Bristol Kingsmen]]\n|[[Bristol, Rhode Island]]\n|Classic\n|1922\n|\n|-\n|[[Broadcasters (drum corps)|Broadcasters]]\n|[[Newton, New Jersey]]\n|Classic/Modern\n|1957&ndash;1972\n|\n|-\n|[[Bro